    v0 = wp.cos((wp.cos(v0 + 0.21) * (tmp + 0.33 + v1 + 0.68)))
    v2 = v2
    v2 = (wp.cos(0.97) * wp.cos(tmp))
    v2 = (wp.sin((v2 + 0.15 / v2 + 0.94)) / (wp.abs(v1 + 0.53) * wp.abs(tmp + 0.17)))
    v2 = 0.46
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.abs(wp.sin(v2 + 0.62)))
